  "info": {
    "title": "Vizgql.Console",
    "version": "0.0.8",
    "description": "The goal of this project is to have a tool for vizualizing and testing\n            authorization for GraphQL schemas. It is not always clear and easy to vizualize\n            how authorization constraints (roles/policies) are applied fields. This\n            projects aims to give you tools to automatically test this, and genrate vizualisations."
  },
